'''Érica Sofia de Jesus Chissapa Bicho''' (yavutse ku ya 22 Ukuboza 1988), uzwi cyane nka '''Erica Chissapa''', ni umukinnyi wa filime akaba n'umunyamakuru [[Angola|wa Angola]]<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3977779/bio</ref> .   Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime''[[:en:Njinga:_Queen_of_Angola|Njinga: Queen of Angola]]'', ''Voo Directo'' and ''Jikulumessu''<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/erica-chissapa/3030497069/</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 22 Ukuboza 1988 i Huambo, mu kibaya cyo hagati cya [[Angola]] <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/erica-chissapa</ref>. Nyuma yaje kwimukira i Luanda afite imyaka ibiri gusa kandi abana na ba sekuruza, asize ababyeyi be na barumuna be batatu mu gihugu cye<ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/erica-chissapa</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 14, Erica yinjiye mu ikinamico. Mugihe yari mu myitozo yitsinda ryamakinamico i Luanda, yatumiriwe gusimbura umwe mubakinnyi bakinnye, wagombaga gufungura nyuma yiminsi itatu<ref>https://www.jornaldeangola.ao/ao/noticias/erica-chissapa-em-novela-portuguesa/</ref>. Hanyuma yimukiye kuri seri ya televiziyo abitumiwe n'umukinnyi Orlando Sérgio . Ariko, ntabwo yatsinze ikizamini cyambere.<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Orlando_S%C3%A9rgio</ref> Nyuma yaje gutsinda guhitamo miniseries, ariko ikibabaje nuko umusaruro wahagaritswe nyuma yimitwe ibiri yanditswe<ref>https://fontedenoticias.com/en/conheca-o-percurso-destas-tres-actrizes-angolanas/</ref>. Icyakora, yakomeje kwigaragaza mu ikinamico ya [[Angola]] hamwe nitsinda ryamakinamico 'Henriques Artes'<ref>https://sw.shops-net.com/136678/1/erica-chissapa.html</ref>. 

Mu 2005, yakinnye muri opera yisabune ''Sede de Viver'' anakina nka 'Kátia'. Intsinzi imaze gutsinda, yatumiwe kugira uruhare runini muri Brezil-Angola ''ikorana na Minha''<ref>https://angorussia.com/entretenimento/fama/erica-chissapa-partilha-emocao-por-ver-a-mae-a-casar-se-com-seu-vestido/</ref> ''Terra Minha Mãe'' . Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakinnye muri filimi ya [[Porutigali|Porutugali]] - Angola ''Voo Directo'' . Muri uruhererekane, Érica yagize uruhare nka 'Weza Oliveira'. Muri 2014, yatumiriwe kujya mu ikinamico ''Jikulumessu'' n'umuririmbyi Coréon Dú<ref>https://alchetron.com/Lesliana-Pereira</ref> . 

